        "version_name": "圣经当代译本",
        "lang": "chs",
        "text": "妇人说：“古时候人们常说，‘有事到亚比拉去请教，问题都会解决。’"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "婦人說：“古時人常說：‘只要在亞比拉求問，事就必成全。’"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "婦人說：「古時有話說，當先在亞比拉求問，然後事就定妥。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then she spoke, saying, “Formerly they used to say, ‘They will surely ask advice at Abel,’ and thus they ended the dispute."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "She continued, “Long ago they used to say, ‘Get your answer at Abel,’ and that settled it."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then she continued, “There used to be a saying, ‘If you want to settle an argument, ask advice at the town of Abel.’"
      }
